  "description": "A really large and roomy French-door refrigerator, introduced to the market by the popular Samsung brand in 2024 and positioned by the manufacturer in the upper price segment. The total useful capacity of the device is 674 liters. The model belongs to the BeSpoke design line. The door trim is replaceable, while the manufacturer offers many options for facade shades that can be used in various combinations. The cooling zone is equipped with an AutoFill water dispenser, the removable jug has a filter for loading fruit pieces. The roomy Samsung BeSpoke RF24BB620EB1 refrigerator is additionally equipped with a combined Dual Ice Maker ice generator, which allows you to create both large and small cubes. Ice is dosed with a spatula. The freezing chamber is a separate pull-out drawer with a capacity of 187 liters. The refrigeration chamber has a volume of 487 liters. There is a SmartThings remote control and management system. Advanced Twin Cooling Plus technology is used to supply cold. The operating noise of the refrigerator does not exceed 38 dB. Energy consumption is at the level of 338 kWh per year.",
